<item>
            <title>[LU-18087] Support encrypted names in changelogs</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18087</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Changelogs are not really up to date regarding support of encrypted files, and the feature needs to be fixed. For instance, the &apos;raw&apos; file name is put in the changelog record and returned to the changelogs consumer, whereas it should be &apos;un-escaped&apos; (as it was escaped to be stored on disk) and encoded for presentation.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
